zhoneVoiceStatsRecords.name: zhoneVoiceStatsRecords
zhoneVoiceStatsRecords.contactinfo: Postal: Zhone Technologies, Inc. @ Zhone Way 7001 Oakport Street Oakland, CA 94621 USA Toll-Free: +1 877-ZHONE20 (+1 877-946-6320) Tel: +1-510-777-7000 Fax: +1-510-777-7001 E-mail: support@zhone.com
zhoneVoiceStatsRecords.description: The MIB module to describe objects for voice call statistics. This MIB record contains tables that define voice calls statistics at the system, card, and subscriber end-point level for incoming, outgoing, and active calls.

zhoneVoiceStats.name: zhoneVoiceStats
zhoneVoiceStats.description: Voice Call Statistics. This Object contains all instances associated with voice calls statistics. In revision 0, Completed, Blocked, and Active calls Statistics are implemented for System, card, and subscriber end-points.

zhoneSystemStats.name: zhoneSystemStats
zhoneSystemStats.description: The System voice statistics object is used to collect voice statistics at a system-wide level. These include statistics for incoming, outgoing, and active calls. The entry in this object is referenced using a static index of zero.

systemIncomingCallsCompleted.name: systemIncomingCallsCompleted
systemIncomingCallsCompleted.description: The number of completed incoming calls in the system.

systemIncomingCallsBlocked.name: systemIncomingCallsBlocked
systemIncomingCallsBlocked.description: The number of blocked incoming calls in the system.

systemOutgoingCallsCompleted.name: systemOutgoingCallsCompleted
systemOutgoingCallsCompleted.description: The number of completed outgoing calls in the system.

systemOutgoingCallsBlocked.name: systemOutgoingCallsBlocked
systemOutgoingCallsBlocked.description: The number of blocked outgoing calls in the system.

systemActiveCalls.name: systemActiveCalls
systemActiveCalls.description: The number of currently active calls in the system.

zhoneCardStatsTable.name: zhoneCardStatsTable
zhoneCardStatsTable.description: The card voice statistics table is used to collect voice calls statistics on any card configured to carry voice traffic. Statistics are currently supported for cards with AAL2, GR303, V52 and POTS subscribers. This table collects statistics for incoming calls, outgoing calls, and active calls. The entry in this table is referenced using shelf/slot indices.

cardIncomingCallsCompleted.name: cardIncomingCallsCompleted
cardIncomingCallsCompleted.description: The number of completed incoming calls on the card.

cardIncomingCallsBlocked.name: cardIncomingCallsBlocked
cardIncomingCallsBlocked.description: The number of blocked incoming calls on the card.

cardOutgoingCallsCompleted.name: cardOutgoingCallsCompleted
cardOutgoingCallsCompleted.description: The number of completed outgoing calls on the card.

cardOutgoingCallsBlocked.name: cardOutgoingCallsBlocked
cardOutgoingCallsBlocked.description: The number of blocked outgoing calls on the card.

cardActiveCalls.name: cardActiveCalls
cardActiveCalls.description: The number of currently active calls on the card.

zhoneSubscriberEPStatsTable.name: zhoneSubscriberEPStatsTable
zhoneSubscriberEPStatsTable.description: The subscriber voice end-point statistics table is used to collect incoming, outgoing, and active voice calls statistics for any subscriber end point.The entry in this table is referenced using end-point index.

subVoiceEndPointIndex.name: subVoiceEndPointIndex
subVoiceEndPointIndex.description: This index is equal to the end-point indices defined for the subscriber voice end-point tables in the zhoneSubscriberRecords. These end-points include AAL2, GR303, V52, POTS, etc. For all the end point types, the end-point index is unique to the sytem.

subEPIncomingCallsCompleted.name: subEPIncomingCallsCompleted
subEPIncomingCallsCompleted.description: The number of completed incoming calls at the subscriber voice end point.

subEPIncomingCallsBlocked.name: subEPIncomingCallsBlocked
subEPIncomingCallsBlocked.description: The number of blocked incoming calls at the subscriber voice end point.

subEPOutgoingCallsCompleted.name: subEPOutgoingCallsCompleted
subEPOutgoingCallsCompleted.description: The number of completed outgoing calls at the subscriber voice end point.

subEPOutgoingCallsBlocked.name: subEPOutgoingCallsBlocked
subEPOutgoingCallsBlocked.description: The number of blocked outgoing calls at the subscriber voice end point.

subEPActiveCalls.name: subEPActiveCalls
subEPActiveCalls.description: The number of currently active calls at the subscriber voice end point.

zhoneVoiceStatsObjectsGroup.name: zhoneVoiceStatsObjectsGroup
zhoneVoiceStatsObjectsGroup.description: This group contains objects associated with voice statistics.

zhoneVoiceRingTable.name: zhoneVoiceRingTable
zhoneVoiceRingTable.description: Table used to generate ring on a port.

zhoneVoiceRingEntry.name: zhoneVoiceRingEntry
zhoneVoiceRingEntry.description: Row in the zhoneVoiceRing table - corresponds to a port on which ring can be generated.

zhoneVoiceRingRingingCadence.name: zhoneVoiceRingRingingCadence
zhoneVoiceRingRingingCadence.description: Ringing cadence to use in test.

zhoneVoiceRingTimer.name: zhoneVoiceRingTimer
zhoneVoiceRingTimer.description: Time in seconds to continue ringing.
